skins.name: Default
skins.secIdle1Text: Commander, want to work out a bit? Sitting for so long is terrible for your body!
skins.secIdle2Text: I thought we were going for some long distance trip at Wake Island again.
skins.secIdle3Text: I swear it wasn't my tummy making that noise!
skins.secTouchText: Are you helping me recover? ... Thank you...
skins.secSpecialTouchText: ...!! Hey! There's a line you shouldn't cross when giving massages.
